# 🎯 GATE Mock Test Generation & Analytics Platform

A full-stack web application that dynamically generates balanced GATE Computer Science (CSE) and GATE Data Science & Artificial Intelligence (DA) mock tests using a rule-based generation engine, evaluates student performance, and provides topic-wise analytics.
Instead of serving fixed mock papers, the platform assembles each test by selecting questions from a structured question bank while following predefined blueprint and difficulty rules to closely resemble the actual GATE examination.

---

## 📌 Features

### 📝 Intelligent Mock Test Generation
- Dynamic mock generation based on GATE blueprint
- Balanced difficulty distribution (Easy / Medium / Hard)
- Topic-wise question allocation
- Randomized question selection
- Support for MCQ, MSQ and NAT questions
- Timed mocktest

### 📚 Question Management
- Structured question bank
- Topic-wise organization
- Difficulty tagging
- Previous Year Questions (PYQs)
- Curated practice questions

### 📊 Performance Analytics
- Automatic evaluation
- Score calculation
- Accuracy Percentage
- Attempt history

### 👤 Users Features
- User authentication
- Generate mock tests
- Attempt exams
- View results
- Performance dashboard

