# 🚀 Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/gate-mock-platform.git
```

```bash
cd gate-mock-platform
```

---

## Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

Activate:

Windows

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

Linux/Mac

```bash
source venv/bin/activate
```

---

## Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Configure Environment

Create a `.env` file.

Example:

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://username:password@localhost:5432/gate_exam
```

---

## Run Backend

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

---

## Run Frontend

```bash
npm install
```

```bash
npm start
```

